ultiple devices including MacBook and iPhone.\",\n                price: 12.90,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F49f266f7bfd61becee4bd8acfc8ff25f_d805d5f7-ed21-468d-9176-9904924af535.jpg%3Fv%3D1752652968&feedId=109349&k=20e0defbb7b3e000453127f1f6026035a0d4f45f\",\n                category: \"Adapters\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461630&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 10,\n                name: \"Acer Dock_option ODK450 Acer SD 4.0 Card Reader, UHS-II Micro SD Reader USB C\",\n                description: \"Dual slot memory card reader with 100W PD port for fast data transfer and charging simultaneously.\",\n                price: 24.90,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F1_05009b39-3012-4ed2-a2e2-6b4b82348447.jpg%3Fv%3D1752653895&feedId=109349&k=92ef7cdb2cd6d8f73533e06e5fa6a9ebb36408a0\",\n                category: \"Adapters\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461637&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 11,\n                name: \"Acer OHR543 Bluetooth Wireless Earbuds Sports Running Gaming Ultra-long Life Long Wear Without Pain\",\n                description: \"ACS cowouchov STEREO, Panoramic sound effects. 5.4 Core wireless: Strong internal 'core' is the driving force. Al call noise reduction: like face-to-face communication.\",\n                price: 39.99,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F543-02.jpg%3Fv%3D1747480076&feedId=109349&k=0bbfbb9ed421308f6dda95612fd7ee61a8aead94\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461549&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 12,\n                name: \"Acer OHR539 Wireless Earbuds Hanging Ear Sports Running Sweat Proof High Quality HIFI Audiophile Headphones\",\n                description: \"Premium wireless earbuds designed for sports and running with sweat-proof technology and high-quality HIFI sound.\",\n                price: 69.00,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F3034a1133efe01daba919094b70c6310.jpg%3Fv%3D1751439203&feedId=109349&k=ef5d27d0b6e9dbc41f5892d97538ec1e9f2a7178\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461552&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 13,\n                name: \"Acer OHR501 Wireless Earbuds 2025 New Mini Invisible Sleep Headset\",\n                description: \"Comfortable good sound quality. Sensorless wearing. High definition calling. Directional sound transmission technology.\",\n                price: 39.00,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F1_860dcea1-d79a-44f2-959c-28e086dc59a6.jpg%3Fv%3D1751439981&feedId=109349&k=5727a7abdf0f17f47cbdbf8ceaac53c3f2d07891\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461554&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 14,\n                name: \"Acer OHR503 Bluetooth Wireless Earbuds Lightweight Immersive Sound Quality Long Wear Without Pain\",\n                description: \"Lightweight wireless earbuds with immersive sound quality designed for long wearing comfort without pain.\",\n                price: 29.90,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F3034a1133efe01daba919094b70c6310_d73890bd-6603-4ad2-b7cf-8eb2520e44f8.jpg%3Fv%3D1751872358&feedId=109349&k=25593cba4bdd80f562cacbaf769d5859463ec358\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461557&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 15,\n                name: \"Acer OHR504 Bluetooth Wireless Earbuds Noise Cancellation Immersive Audio Experience Long Wear Without Pain\",\n                description: \"Noise cancellation wireless earbuds with immersive audio experience designed for long wearing comfort.\",\n                price: 34.90,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F3034a1133efe01daba919094b70c6310_8ad8ab07-8596-4e6f-a104-5dd81e17c964.jpg%3Fv%3D1751872394&feedId=109349&k=40be89df7f7d6737224a6f301bf693b86f1dc6da\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461560&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 16,\n                name: \"Acer OHR508 Bluetooth Wireless Earbuds Multiple Noise Reduction Surround Sound Long Wear Without Pain\",\n                description: \"Multiple noise reduction wireless earbuds with surround sound technology for long wearing comfort.\",\n                price: 59.00,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F3034a1133efe01daba919094b70c6310_4a9feb6b-df3f-46dd-809b-373c893edf5c.jpg%3Fv%3D1751878861&feedId=109349&k=440681586a73fa3cdd6896b8e71f70cf80013d79\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461563&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 17,\n                name: \"Acer OHR513 Wireless Earbuds 2025 New Mini Invisible Sleep Headset Small Size Stable And Faster\",\n                description: \"Mini invisible sleep headset with small size design for stable and faster connection.\",\n                price: 49.00,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F49f266f7bfd61becee4bd8acfc8ff25f_792d6f1e-75cb-4517-a562-213f961b914b.jpg%3Fv%3D1751448216&feedId=109349&k=b8c9f9531a41fc755c1bc8f22e433dea65e67e05\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461566&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 18,\n                name: \"Acer OHR514 Wireless Earbuds Hanging Ear Sports Running Special 2025 New High Sound Quality Long Life Bass HIFI\",\n                description: \"Hanging ear sports running earbuds with special 2025 new high sound quality and long life bass HIFI.\",\n                price: 69.00,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F2_77ff6107-fea5-47b6-9b01-fef797a5ebfb.jpg%3Fv%3D1751879584&feedId=109349&k=c4590a8402c29318a4e35063458bb40fe55d1108\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461569&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            },\n            {\n                id: 19,\n                name: \"Acer OHR515 Wireless Earbuds Hanging Ear Sports Running Special 2025 New High Sound Quality LED Power Display Leather Texture\",\n                description: \"Hanging ear sports running earbuds with LED power display and leather texture for premium look.\",\n                price: 69.00,\n                image: \"https://images2.productserve.com/?w=200&h=200&bg=white&trim=5&t=letterbox&url=ssl%3Acdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0643%2F0343%2F1859%2Ffiles%2F49f266f7bfd61becee4bd8acfc8ff25f_e808cfc3-c303-4eb8-9259-1dae386c6545.jpg%3Fv%3D1751449735&feedId=109349&k=c50eb2ffd9a2008981afeeab9343619ef9abbf61\",\n                category: \"Wireless Earbuds\",\n                brand: \"Acer\",\n                inStock: true,\n                link: \"https://www.awin1.com/pclick.php?p=42224461572&a=1923681&m=118307\"\n            }\n        ];\n\n        // Application State\n        let products = [];\n        let filteredProducts = [];\n        let filters = {\n            category: [],\n            brand: [],\n            maxPrice: 100,\n            inStock: true,\n            searchQuery: ''\n        };\n\n        // DOM Elements\n        const productGrid = document.getElementById('productGrid');\n        const resultsCount = document.getElementById('resultsCount');\n        const searchBox = document.getElementById('searchBox');\n        const priceSlider = document.getElementById('priceSlider');\n        const maxPriceDisplay = document.getElementById('maxPriceDisplay');\n        const inStockFilter = document.getElementById('inStockFilter');\n        const sortSelect = document.getElementById('sortSelect');\n        const clearFiltersBtn = document.getElementById('clearFilters');\n        const categoryFilter = document.getElementById('categoryFilter');\n        const brandFilter = document.getElementById('brandFilter');\n        const mobileFiltersToggle = document.getElementById('mobileFiltersToggle');\n        const filtersSidebar = document.getElementById('filtersSidebar');\n        const filtersOverlay = document.getElementById('filtersOverlay');\n\n        // Initialize the application\n        function init() {\n            products = productData;\n            filteredProducts = [...products];\n            \n            // Extract unique categories and brands for filters\n            const categories = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.category))];\n            const brands = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.brand))];\n            \n            // Build filter options\n            buildFilterOptions(categories, categoryFilter, 'category');\n            buildFilterOptions(brands, brandFilter, 'brand');\n            \n            // Set max price for slider\n            const maxPrice = Math.max(...products.map(p => p.price));\n            priceSlider.max = Math.ceil(maxPrice);\n            priceSlider.value = Math.ceil(maxPrice);\n            updatePriceDisplay();\n            \n            // Set initial filter values\n            filters.maxPrice = Math.ceil(maxPrice);\n            \n            // Render initial products\n            renderProducts();\n            \n            // Set up event listeners\n            setupEventListeners();\n        }\n\n        // Build filter option checkboxes\n        function buildFilterOptions(items, container, filterType) {\n            container.innerHTML = '';\n            \n            items.forEach(item => {\n                if (!item) return;\n                \n                const option = document.createElement('div');\n                option.className = 'filter-option';\n                option.innerHTML = `\n                    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"${filterType}-${item.replace(/\\s+/g, '-')}\" checked>\n                    <label for=\"${filterType}-${item.replace(/\\s+/g, '-')}\">${item}</label>\n                `;\n                container.appendChild(option);\n                \n                const checkbox = option.querySelector('input');\n                checkbox.addEventListener('change', () => {\n                    if (checkbox.checked) {\n                        filters[filterType].push(item);\n                    } else {\n                        filters[filterType] = filters[filterType].filter(f => f !== item);\n                    }\n                    filterProducts();\n                });\n                \n                // Add to initial filters\n                filters[filterType].push(item);\n            });\n        }\n\n        // Update price display\n        function updatePriceDisplay() {\n            const maxPrice = priceSlider.value;\n            maxPriceDisplay.textContent = maxPrice >= priceSlider.max ? `$${maxPrice}+` : `$${maxPrice}`;\n            filters.maxPrice = parseInt(maxPrice);\n            filterProducts();\n        }\n\n        // Filter products based on current filters\n        function filterProducts() {\n            filteredProducts = products.filter(product => {\n                // Search filter\n                if (filters.searchQuery) {\n                    const query = filters.searchQuery.toLowerCase();\n                    const inName = product.name.toLowerCase().includes(query);\n                    const inDesc = product.description.toLowerCase().includes(query);\n                    const inCategory = product.category.toLowerCase().includes(query);\n                    if (!inName && !inDesc && !inCategory) return false;\n                }\n                \n                // Category filter\n                if (filters.category.length > 0 && !filters.category.includes(product.category)) {\n                    return false;\n                }\n                \n                // Brand filter\n                if (filters.brand.length > 0 && !filters.brand.includes(product.brand)) {\n                    return false;\n                }\n                \n                // Price filter\n                if (product.price > filters.maxPrice) {\n                    return false;\n                }\n                \n                // Availability filter\n                if (filters.inStock && !product.inStock) {\n                    return false;\n                }\n                \n                return true;\n            });\n            \n            // Apply sorting\n            applySorting();\n            \n            // Update results count\n            resultsCount.textContent = `Showing ${filteredProducts.length} of ${products.length} products`;\n            \n            // Re-render products\n            renderProducts();\n        }\n\n        // Apply sorting to filtered products\n        function applySorting() {\n            const sortValue = sortSelect.value;\n            \n            switch(sortValue) {\n                case 'price-low':\n                    filteredProducts.sort((a, b) => a.price - b.price);\n                    break;\n                case 'price-high':\n                    filteredProducts.sort((a, b) => b.price - a.price);\n                    break;\n                case 'name':\n                    filteredProducts.sort((a, b) => a.name.localeCompare(b.name));\n                    break;\n                default:\n                    // Default sorting (by ID or original order)\n                    filteredProducts.sort((a, b) => a.id - b.id);\n                    break;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Render products to the grid\n        function renderProducts() {\n            if (filteredProducts.length === 0) {\n                productGrid.innerHTML = `\n                    <div style=\"grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; padding: 3rem; color: var(--gray);\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-search\" style=\"font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"></i>\n                        <h3>No products found</h3>\n                        <p>Try adjusting your filters or search terms</p>\n                    </div>\n                `;\n                return;\n            }\n            \n            productGrid.innerHTML = '';\n            \n            filteredProducts.forEach(product => {\n                const productCard = document.createElement('div');\n                productCard.className = 'product-card';\n                \n                // Format price\n                const formattedPrice = product.price === 0 ? 'Check Price' : `$${product.price.toFixed(2)}`;\n                \n                // Create badge for free products\n                const badge = product.price === 0 ? '<div class=\"product-badge\">Check Price</div>' : '';\n                \n                productCard.innerHTML = `\n                    <div class=\"product-image-container\">\n                        ${badge}\n                        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"${product.image}\" alt=\"${product.name}\" class=\"product-image\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"product-content\">\n                        <h3 class=\"product-title\">${product.name}</h3>\n                        <p class=\"product-description\">${product.description}</p>\n                        <div class=\"product-price\">${formattedPrice}</div>\n                        <a href=\"${product.link}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"buy-button\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-shopping-cart\"></i> Buy Now\n                        </a>\n                        <div class=\"product-meta\">\n                            <span>${product.category}</span>\n                            <span>${product.brand}</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                `;\n                \n                productGrid.appendChild(productCard);\n            });\n        }\n\n        // Set up event listeners\n        function setupEventListeners() {\n            // Search box\n            searchBox.addEventListener('input', (e) => {\n                filters.searchQuery = e.target.value;\n                filterProducts();\n            });\n            \n            // Price slider\n            priceSlider.addEventListener('input', updatePriceDisplay);\n            \n            // In stock filter\n            inStockFilter.addEventListener('change', (e) => {\n                filters.inStock = e.target.checked;\n                filterProducts();\n            });\n            \n            // Sort select\n            sortSelect.addEventListener('change', () => {\n                applySorting();\n                renderProducts();\n            });\n            \n            // Clear filters\n            clearFiltersBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                // Reset all checkboxes\n                document.querySelectorAll('.filter-option input').forEach(checkbox => {\n                    checkbox.checked = true;\n                });\n                \n                // Reset search\n                searchBox.value = '';\n                \n                // Reset price slider\n                const maxPrice = Math.max(...products.map(p => p.price));\n                priceSlider.value = Math.ceil(maxPrice);\n                \n                // Reset filters state\n                filters = {\n                    category: [...new Set(products.map(p => p.category))],\n                    brand: [...new Set(products.map(p => p.brand))],\n                    maxPrice: Math.ceil(maxPrice),\n                    inStock: true,\n                    searchQuery: ''\n                };\n                \n                // Update display\n                updatePriceDisplay();\n                filterProducts();\n            });\n            \n            // Mobile filters toggle\n            mobileFiltersToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                filtersSidebar.classList.add('active');\n                filtersOverlay.classList.add('active');\n            });\n            \n            // Close filters on overlay click\n            filtersOverlay.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                filtersSidebar.classList.remove('active');\n                filtersOverlay.classList.remove('active');\n            });\n            \n            // Lazy load images\n            const lazyLoadImages = () => {\n                const imageObservers = [];\n                \n                document.querySelectorAll('.product-image').forEach(img => {\n                    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                        entries.forEach(entry => {\n                            if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                                const lazyImage = entry.target;\n                                lazyImage.src = lazyImage.getAttribute('src');\n                                imageObservers.forEach(obs => obs.unobserve(lazyImage));\n                            }\n                        });\n                    });\n                    \n                    observer.observe(img);\n                    imageObservers.push(observer);\n                });\n            };\n            \n            // Initial lazy load\n            setTimeout(lazyLoadImages, 100);\n            \n            // Re-lazy load after filtering\n            const originalFilterProducts = filterProducts;\n            filterProducts = function() {\n                originalFilterProducts.apply(this);\n                setTimeout(lazyLoadImages, 100);\n            };\n        }\n\n        // Initialize when DOM is loaded\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', init);\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}